description:
In this karaoke version of "The longer I serve him," you'll be singing along with the key of G# as you worship God!
This hymn is a great way to express your gratitude for all that God has done for you.Whether you're a worship leader or just a singer in the choir, this karaoke version of "The longer I serve him" is a fun way to get everyone singing and praising God!

Songwriter: William J. Gaither.
Music performed by C Lalhmuaka, 3 Sisters Youtube Channel
